=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'debug message'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">logger</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">spam</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'spam message'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<p>It just works, and adds <code>--verbose</code> and <code>--quiet</code> command line options, too.</p>\n<h2>Adding other command line parameters</h2>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">scripthelper</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">scripthelper</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">add_argument</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'-n'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'--name'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">help</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'Name to greet'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">logger</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">args</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">scripthelper</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">bootstrap_args</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"n\">args</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">logger</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">debug</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'Name was provided'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">logger</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">info</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"sa\">f</span><span class=\"s1\">'Hello </span><span class=\"si\">{</span><span class=\"n\">args</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"si\">}</span><span class=\"s1\">'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">logger</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">warning</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><sp